Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.49,0:01:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪客劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.47,0:01:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥手腕中了御庭番高手\N惡見的毒螺旋鏢生命垂危
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧惠姑娘指點才完全康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.91,0:01:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是害死左之助朋友中的鴉片\N竟然是惠姑娘做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.62,0:02:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘是受到\N武田觀柳逼迫才做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.36,0:02:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但即使是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.66,0:02:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助還是無法原諒惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘受到觀柳威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.90,0:02:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護我們\N抱著必死之心回到觀柳身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.38,0:02:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助瞭解惠姑娘的心意\N為阻止她打倒了式尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是惠姑娘還是被帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.44,0:02:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心和我們\N便決心要救出惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.44,0:02:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十話\N蒼紫俊美過人的恐怖人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.99,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘在那堶情I
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一口氣衝到門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開！讓開！\N劍心四人組來也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚷嚷什麼，可惡的傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.65,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來，惠姑娘\N我早料到你一定會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.36,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事不宜遲，請開始做鴉片吧\N好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再反抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.34,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該有所覺悟才回來的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.78,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要活著才能贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.15,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天能和你家人見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了就什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.22,0:04:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我除了這麼做又能怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經覺悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.46,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的覺悟是先殺了你\N再自我了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經幫你解危了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.91,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這丫頭！對她好還不領情\N想跟我耍花招，殺了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.99,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過殺她之前\N先拷問出新型鴉片的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.16,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣說不定比死還痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了。。。那男的是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是一般人的功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.85,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你們可看清楚\N我們要上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！好強。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倆人搭檔實在太強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.06,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.66,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，是四人搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要看輕我們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍兵隊準備射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然毫不畏懼加速往前衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是現在，射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.08,0:05:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥，快跳\N讓他嘗嘗我們的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛，可惡！。。哇啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.93,0:06:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然啦！喂！\N左之助剛剛你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我給你機會表現啊\N不用謝啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個人都很有精神嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.65,0:06:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真搞不懂，到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.95,0:06:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齋是為了什麼好處\N願意為那女的效命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.33,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬人拔刀齋如果為利益所動\N現在已經做到軍方幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的人你是無法理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼？現在要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.64,0:06:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少說\N對手是傳說中的斬人劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們處境太危陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交稅時間到了\N武田觀柳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是來帶回惠姑娘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！真厲害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.27,0:07:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能一下子打倒這麼多人\N真不愧是傳說的斬人拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人怎麼知道劍心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番高手幫他查的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了！你的功夫我很欣賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.92,0:07:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能加入御庭番為我效命\N我是再放心不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.76,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我付你我手下五十人份酬勞\N你覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會把你當心腹看待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底要下來還是不下來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.24,0:07:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。一百人份！\N二。。二百人份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.54,0:07:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧！他不為利益所動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話！你給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.15,0:08:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了！我輸了！我投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會放了高荷惠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們需要有點準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我一個小時\N我一定交人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們就站在那堣ㄜn動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這白癡到底在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.34,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，一個小時就能逼\N高荷惠說出新型鴉片的做法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘我們自己來帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你乖乖等著吧！觀柳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.14,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來緩兵策略無效\N反而更激怒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此\N就給拔刀齋點顏色瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.65,0:09:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這麼說你清楚了吧？般若\N養你們御庭番就是為防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再有惡見和火男那樣的錯誤\N我絕不原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別搞錯了，觀柳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有首領能命令我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番還輪不到\N像你這種人來命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.94,0:09:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能命令我們的\N只有首領四乃森蒼紫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.88,0:09:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了教頭我們樂意效死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為是誰重聘你們首領的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.76,0:09:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連你們首領都不敢對我說不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定會打倒拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是堂堂首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過可不是為了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.61,0:10:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了證明我們御庭番最強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.18,0:10:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種為錢而死的人\N是無法理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.49,0:10:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新志士與我們的立場不同\N是為了自己理想殉命的一群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.03,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了明治時代\N很多志士都消聲匿跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.33,0:10:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那傢伙竟然還存活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.87,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔了十年再出現令人刮目\N那傢伙是我們的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是也應該保護我啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種人渣\N你知道會怎樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什。。。什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.75,0:10:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方要的是高荷惠\N把這女的關到三樓展望室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若，你馬上就去佈置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.99,0:10:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我。。。我怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.50,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這堥蘑躁せ好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可。。。可惡的四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.11,0:11:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這媔}始\N應該有御庭番高手陣守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少廢話，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.26,0:11:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶城御庭番高手密探般若
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉首領之命在此死守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.19,0:12:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神谷道場那些人\N已經來這堶n把你搶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心先生他們？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.13,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過你不要抱無謂的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正他們也到不了這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.07,0:12:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你眼前的不是獲救\N而是被觀柳拷問而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.91,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是你的短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.28,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要痛苦的活或安樂的死\N你自己選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.59,0:12:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想有無謂的打鬥\N能不能請你讓開？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領的命令必須遵從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.70,0:12:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋，皮手袋下穿著鐵甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！那個招勢是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他使出的是拳法。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.85,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間寶貴\N不用客氣請使出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.22,0:13:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也一樣，我出招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要直接攻擊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻形拳！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是看走眼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嘛慢吞吞的被打\N這不像你啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流第十八招\N「讀招」不管用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.59,0:13:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我確實有及時閃過\N也讀出他的拳法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.13,0:13:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他的手腕\N在我眼前突然伸長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣？拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的能耐應不只如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.27,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連我般若的幻術都攻不破\N與首領打的話是毫無勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻術？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.35,0:14:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一開始觀察我的招數時\N我已神不知鬼不覺使出幻術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已經開打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,般若用的是伸腕幻術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.37,0:14:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不出破綻，拔刀齋絕無勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是用幻術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.18,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下麻煩了\N非得先破解幻術不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！那是什麼招勢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道耶！\N看起來很像正眼招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對！是信劍招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被稱為自信劍法的信劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不管對方做何變化\N都能立即對應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是古代劍術的堅強防禦招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.37,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然用信劍！\N難以攻擊時轉為防禦的招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.94,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齋竟想得到用這招勢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.88,0:15:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男的\N就是傳說的斬人劍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.45,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種能耐\N根本沒資格和蒼紫大人打！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.42,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我般若在此就能把你解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.33,0:15:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論信劍招勢防禦有多堅固\N要破解伸腕幻術是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.77,0:15:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破解了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.15,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看出他幻術的破綻了嗎\N劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.52,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幻術的真面目\N是他手腕露出的橫條刺青
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橫條刺青。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.79,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此！\N橫條會引起眼睛的錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓東西看起來比實際還大\N這就是你目測錯誤的原因嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.63,0:16:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可。。。可惡那信劍的招勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來不是為了防守\N而是要測出手腕的實際長度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是用逆刃刀當尺量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是拔刀齋。。\N看來我太低估你了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.99,0:16:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今經歷無數的殘酷戰役\N地獄的模樣我也目睹過幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我相信首領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.87,0:16:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了證明御庭番\N是江戶最強才前來與你較量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了我們的名譽\N非得打倒拔刀齋你不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鉤爪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.09,0:16:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓惠姑娘當人質\N你們有何名譽可言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住。。。住口！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,憑你這點能耐。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.84,0:17:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本敵不過蒼紫大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘危在旦夕\N我先進去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙不是一般的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只他\N還有式尉、惡見、火男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.20,0:17:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人的首領那個叫蒼紫的人\N到底是何等人物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的傷沒關係吧？劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小傷而已！已經止血了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你們再進去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！你們擺好架勢啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.29,0:18:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心、左之助\N你們快去救惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！讓他倆應付應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！那熏姑娘、禰彥，拜託你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.89,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就憑這小丫頭和小毛頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少侮辱人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們見識神谷活心流的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可別看輕我們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！這就是他們說的首領？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.26,0:18:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男的是江戶城御庭番的首領\N四乃森蒼紫。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳與惠姑娘人在哪堙H
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.37,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想知道他們兩人在哪傜N要問我的刀，拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就用它來回答你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.95,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！憑那把刀\N想挑戰劍心別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.06,0:19:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目標\N只有拔刀齋你閃到一邊去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.36,0:19:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！可惡\N就讓我來殺殺你銳氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象打倒式尉一樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著！左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不自量力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！振作點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一拳就能打倒左之助。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後要乖乖聽別人的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.03,0:19:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來輪到你了，拔刀齋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.56,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小太刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！界於刀與小刀間的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比刀短雖然攻勢力較差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.37,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因刀輕防禦力極高\N能當盾牌用的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.64,0:20:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小太刀雖然善於防守\N卻不利於攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，這傢伙。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫重視防守嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.65,0:20:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.52,0:20:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？拔刀齋\N由我開始進攻嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身手真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.43,0:20:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這男的和般若一樣擅拳法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.72,0:20:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來！用太小刀做劍壁防守\N再用和般若相同的拳法攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.99,0:20:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點別搞錯了\N般若的拳法可是我教他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.17,0:21:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的拳法速度\N與師弟完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果以為一樣就太低估我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。。。劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.38,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙。。。說不定大有來頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.32,0:21:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼厲害的人。。。\N到底是為了什麼。。。

